<div class="hlist">
<ul>
<li>(<a href="/wiki/Racism_in_the_Arab_world" title="Racism in the Arab world">Arab</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/White_supremacy" title="White supremacy">White</a>)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</td>
